### Add product to user cart
PUT http://localhost:4000/user-api/cart/product-id/69ab0a8222a38e90fcf72971


//post request and put requests should send data to the API as body of the request object
//get and delete requests do not support body of the request object
//so that these two requests send data through endpoint




### Read all products
GET http://localhost:4000/product-api/products


### Read product by id
GET http://localhost:4000/product-api/products/102


### Create new Product
POST http://localhost:4000/product-api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId" : 102,
    "productName" : "bottle",
    "price" : 12000,
    "brand" : "stanley"
}


### Update a Product
PUT http://localhost:4000/product-api/products/101
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId" : 101,
    "productName" : "laptop",
    "price" : 48000,
    "brand" : "HP"
}


### Delete a Product
DELETE http://localhost:4000/product-api/products/102
